replaceContent../page/component/index.wxml:
<mp-navigation-bar title="小程序官方组件展示" back="{{false}}" data-ib-structured-id="0"></mp-navigation-bar>
<scroll-view class="page-scroll-view" scroll-y type="list" data-ib-structured-id="1">
<view class="page" data-weui-theme="{{theme}}" data-ib-structured-id="2">
  <view class="index" data-ib-structured-id="3">
    <view class="index-hd" data-ib-structured-id="4">
      <image class="index-logo" src="resources/kind/logo.png" data-ib-structured-id="5"></image>
      <text class="index-desc" data-ib-structured-id="6">以下将展示小程序官方组件能力，组件样式仅供参考，开发者可根据自身需求自定义组件样式，具体属性参数详见 <text class="weui-agree__link" bindtap="navToDoc" data-ib-structured-id="7">小程序开发文档</text>。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="index-bd" data-ib-structured-id="8">
      <view class="kind-list" data-ib-structured-id="9">
        <block wx:for-items="{{list}}" wx:key="{{item.id}}" data-ib-structured-id="10">
          <view class="kind-list-item" data-ib-structured-id="11">
            <view id="{{item.id}}" class="kind-list-item-hd {{item.open ? 'kind-list-item-hd-show' : ''}}" bindtap="kindToggle" data-ib-structured-id="12">
              <view class="kind-list-text" data-ib-structured-id="13">{{item.name}}</view>
              <image wx:if="{{theme === 'dark'}}" class="kind-list-img" src="resources/kind/{{item.id}}_dark.png" data-ib-structured-id="14"></image>
              <image wx:else class="kind-list-img" src="resources/kind/{{item.id}}.png" data-ib-structured-id="15"></image>
            </view>
            <view class="kind-list-item-bd {{item.open ? 'kind-list-item-bd-show' : ''}}" data-ib-structured-id="16">
              <view class="navigator-box {{item.open ? 'navigator-box-show' : ''}}" data-ib-structured-id="17">
                <block wx:for-items="{{item.pages}}" wx:for-item="page" wx:key="*item" data-ib-structured-id="18">
                  <view wx:if="{{page.appid}}" data-ib-structured-id="19">
                    <navigator target="miniProgram" open-type="navigate" app-id="{{page.appid}}" path="" extra-data="" version="release" class="navigator {{index + 1 === item.pages.length ? '' : 'navigator-bottom-line'}}" data-ib-structured-id="20">{{page.name}}</navigator>
                    <view class="navigator-arrow" data-ib-structured-id="21"></view>
                  </view>
                  <!-- custom-route，自定义路由暂时不能用 navigator -->
                  <view wx:elif="{{page.key == 'custom-route'}}" data-ib-structured-id="22">
                    <view bindtap="goToCustomRoute" class="navigator {{index + 1 === item.pages.length ? '' : 'navigator-bottom-line'}}" data-ib-structured-id="23">{{page.name}}</view>
                    <view class="navigator-arrow" data-ib-structured-id="24"></view>
                  </view>
                  <!-- skyline -->
                  <view wx:elif="{{item.id == 'Skyline'}}" data-ib-structured-id="25">
                    <navigator url="/packageSkyline/pages/{{page.url}}" class="navigator {{index + 1 === item.pages.length ? '' : 'navigator-bottom-line'}}" data-ib-structured-id="26">{{page.name}}</navigator>
                    <view class="navigator-arrow" data-ib-structured-id="27"></view>
                  </view>
                  <view wx:else data-ib-structured-id="28">
                    <navigator url="/packageComponent/pages/{{item.id}}/{{page}}/{{page}}" class="navigator {{index + 1 === item.pages.length ? '' : 'navigator-bottom-line'}}" data-ib-structured-id="29">{{page}}</navigator>
                    <view class="navigator-arrow" data-ib-structured-id="30"></view>
                  </view>
                </block>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
</scroll-view>
